name: Orbsu: Music Tap Game
description:
Orbsu is a tapping music/rhythm game developed by Aoxer games. Join our Discord via www.aoxer.io/discord.

If game over happens before the music is completed, your accuracy/performance percentage is reduced according to the proportion of music completed.

Thanks Inova for letting us use his music on our app. For concerns about copyright, contact us at license@aoxer.io.

Rankings: SSS (100%), SS (99%), S (98%), A (95%), B (90%), C (85%), D (70%), E (50%), F (0%).
